name: Crab character sand walk
description: A stop motion animation of a unique crab character making his way along a beach. The stop motion puppet was created by hand with wire, barkcloth, clay and seeds(eyes). This character appeared in the award-winning stop motion film “The Metamorphosis of a Bottle Cap” and belongs to a set of over 80 original puppets created by Kathryn Ann Jankowski. www.katjankowski.com
